{"tid":1892792,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟差對audit狗有咩影響？","createTime":"2020-02-22T18:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T10:23:11.000Z","uid":225818,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a807b76b102c6d6b5311b6689e38b25b7f2c8c9b","tid":1892792,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:37:53.000Z","msg":"話說前度係audit狗<br />\n當年仲要唔係u grad又入唔到大公司既廢柴<br />\n分手之後間唔時都聽聞到佢自己開左公司之類<br />\n最近經濟係差左<br />\n又聽聞到佢出番黎打工<br />\n其實經濟差對做audit呢行既人有咩影響？<br />\n開完公司又要出黎打工 之後會變成點？<br />\n<br />\n條友藍加紅到發紫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當年仲細唔帶眼識人，分手係因為政見不合，當然最後係嘈到不歡而散。分手之後既我發展得好好亦無再深究佢做啲乜，但到今日依然好想睇住條藍絲廢柴節墮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申行外人"},{"pid":"c12a67404a26a15ab4da8a051d19d2825624918a","tid":1892792,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係恭喜佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ce423deeaf6d70a39c7a26c7483a1701902527","tid":1892792,"uid":75823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:40:35.000Z","msg":"audit根本對公司老闆毫無價值, 所以任何時候一定係被壓價"},{"pid":"c1a2cefd0ca28c500cfd0a258821eb81f9af57df","tid":1892792,"uid":147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>audit根本對公司老闆毫無價值, 所以任何時候一定係被壓價</blockquote><br />\n壓到一個點<br />\n唔接大把公司接<br />\n接完又無肉食 份bonus byebye<br />\n凍薪"},{"pid":"948d4f6252af84633869f892e4e215b39453626f","tid":1892792,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c12a67404a26a